re &amp; <a href="https://www.trawell.in/tamilnadu/chennai" target="_blank">Chennai</a>. When the River Kaveri enters the Tamil Nadu border after winding its way through the state of Karnataka, it descends down the lofty landscape forming the Hogenakkal Waterfalls. The Carbonatite rocks found near the waterfall are one of the .....</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row" align="center">\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><a class="btn btn-sm btn-default lnkDirections fleft" href="https://www.trawell.in/tamilnadu/best?more=1#">Get Directions</a></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><a class="btn btn-sm lnkViewDetails fright" title="Hogenakkal - View Details" href="https://www.trawell.in/tamilnadu/hogenakkal" target="_blank">View Details</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="TNKBK_2" class="destContent">\r\n<div class="destDivider">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="destDiv">\r\n<div class="row destTitleDiv">\r\n<div class="col-md-9 destTitleMain">\r\n<h2><a class="destTitle" title="Kumbakonam - View Details" href="https://www.trawell.in/tamilnadu/kumbakonam" target="_blank">Kumbakonam</a></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 destRating" align="right"><img class="imgRating" src="https://www.trawell.in/images/5star_new.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row" align="center">\r\n<div class="col-md-5">\r\n<div class="destImg" align="center"><a href="https://www.trawell.in/admin/images/upload/868291118Kumbakonam_Main.jpg" data-toggle="lightbox" data-gallery="multiimages" data-title="Kumbakonam"><img id="TNKBK_img" class="lazy" title="Enlarge Image" src="https://www.trawell.in/admin/images/thumbs/868291118Kumbakonam_Main_thumb.jpg" align="center" border="0" data-src="/admin/images/thumbs/868291118Kumbakonam_Main_thumb.jpg" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-7 masterDestDesc">\r\n<div class="divDestType" align="left">\r\n<p class="destTitle"><img class="imgDestType" src="https://www.trawell.in/images/icons/icon-PL.png" height="20" /><